<div class="ugc-mod reading-notes">
  <div class="hd">
    <h2>
      读书笔记&nbsp;&nbsp;· · · · · ·&nbsp;
          <span class="pl">(<a href="https://book.douban.com/subject/26325928/annotation">共<span property="v:count">36</span>篇</a>)</span>

    </h2>

      <a class="redbutt rr j a_show_login" href="https://www.douban.com/register?reason=annotate" rel="nofollow"><span>我来写笔记</span></a>
  </div>
  

    <div class="bd">
      <ul class="inline-tabs">
        <li class="on"><a href="#rank" id="by_rank" >按有用程度</a></li>
        <li><a href="#page" id="by_page" >按页码先后</a></li>
        <li><a href="#time" id="by_time" >最新笔记</a></li>
      </ul>
      
  <ul class="comments by_rank" >
      
      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="35055462">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/chikagesophie/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2139351-15.jpg" alt="小砂" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/35055462/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/35055462/" class="">第44页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/chikagesophie/" class=" " title="小砂">小砂</a>
                (头像非本人。)
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="35055462">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <div class="ll">
                    <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/35055462/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/small/public/p35055462-1.jpg"></a>
                  </div>
                  <span class=""> 
其实这一页是四张脚，但借去了这两个比较有故事的。
觉得脚的这部分是整本书比较有意思的一part。我们熟悉人在纽约还是因为各异的面孔，但人生往往是从脚底开始的。对吧？

“光脚走路，最酷的感觉是？”
“生命体验更鲜活，直接感受世间冷暖。”
“那最糟糕的体验呢？”
“踩到屎。”</span>
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/35055462/">(<span class="">3回应</span>)</a>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2015-05-11 12:26</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">5人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <div class="middle"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p35055462-1.jpg" alt=""><br><span class="pic-title"></span></div>
其实这一页是四张脚，但借去了这两个比较有故事的。<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>觉得脚的这部分是整本书比较有意思的一part。我们熟悉人在纽约还是因为各异的面孔，但人生往往是从脚底开始的。对吧？<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div><blockquote><q>“光脚走路，最酷的感觉是？”
“生命体验更鲜活，直接感受世间冷暖。”
“那最糟糕的体验呢？”
“踩到屎。”</q></blockquote>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
